      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "KONNAN CARTEL (6) hasn't raced since finishing ninth over 229m at Listed level at Evangeline Downs (Dirt) on October 4 and has since switched yards. Goes very well when fresh from a spell, scoring on three occasions from five starts. Ready for a bold showing. PAINT ME ONIS (5) returns from a layoff of 11 weeks. Worth noting he filled a minor placing when returning from a spell last time in work over 366m at Evangeline Downs. Has found the right race. TF JESS A EAGLE (8) saluted over 201m at Louisiana Downs (Dirt) at his most recent appearance on February 4. Yet to win first up but generally runs well with two minor placings from four tries. Lines up today for the first time for trainer Erica Arteaga. Sure to make his presence felt. G AMTRAK B (1) has put together back-to-back placings, the latest when 0.3 lengths away in second over 201m at Louisiana Downs (Dirt). Well placed and will be thereabouts again. Something for the Multiples: MP SIXY SILHOUTTE (2)",
